<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100758>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Stenosagola gracilis. a) Winged male antenna, dorsal view, b) Wingless male antenna, dorsal view, c) Female antenna, dorsal view, d) Winged male head, dorsal view, e) Wingless male head, dorsal view, f) Female head, dorsal view, g) Labrum, dorsal view, h) Mentum, ventral view, i) Prothorax, ventral view, j) Scutellum, dorsal view, k) Winged male elytra, dorsal view, l) Wingless male elytra, dorsal view, m) Meso- and metaventrites, ventral view, n) Abdominal tergite VIII, dorsal view, o) Abdominal ventrite VIII, ventral view, p) Winged male abdomen, dorsal view, q) Wingless male abdomen, dorsal view, r) Winged male hind coxa, ventral view, s) Aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100758/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100771>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Stenosagola connata. a) Winged male antenna, dorsal view, b) Wingless male antenna, dorsal view, c) Female antenna, dorsal view, d) Winged male head, dorsal view, e) Wingless male head, dorsal view, f) Female head, dorsal view, g) Prothorax, ventral view, h) Meso- and metaventrites, ventral view, i) Winged male elytra, dorsal view, j) Wingless male elytra, dorsal view, k) Wingled male abdomen, dorsal view, l) Wingless male abdomen, dorsal view, m) Abdominal tergite VIII, dorsal view, n) Abdominal ventrite VIII, ventral view, o) Winged male hind-coxa, ventral view, p) Aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100771/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100762>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Stenosagola species. a) S. pseudogracilis, aedeagus, dorsal view, b) S. clarkei, aedeagus, dorsal view, c) S. egmontensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, d) S. ramsayi, e) S. egmontensis, winged male head, dorsal view; f) S. egmontensis, prothorax, ventral view; g) S. egmontensis, prothoracic leg, h) S. domettensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, i) S. eylesi, aedeagus, dorsal view, j) S. stewartensis, aedeagus, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100762/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100775>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Stenosagola species. a) S. huiaensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, b) S. northlandensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, c) S. thayerae, aedeagus, dorsal view, d) S. dugdalei, aedeagus, dorsal view, e) S. tararuaensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, f) S. haunuiensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, g) S. haunuiensis, wingless male head, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100775/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100781>
    dc:description "Fig. 12. Stenosagola species. a) S. pseudoconnata, aedeagus, dorsal view, b) S. chandleri, aedeagus, dorsal view, c) S. nunni, aedeagus, dorsal view, d) S. newtoni, aedeagus, dorsal view, e) S. butcheri, aedeagus, dorsal view, f) S. fiordlandensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, g) S. fiordlandensis, wingless male head, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100781/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100756>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Habitus of Stenosagola species, dorsal view. a) Winged male of S. gracilis, b) Wingless male of S. gracilis, c) Female of S. gracilis, d) Winged male of S. pseudogracilis, e) Wingless male of S. pseudogracilis, f) Female of S. pseudogracilis, g) Wingless male of S. clarkei, h) Wingless male of S. egmontensis, i) Female of S. egmontensis, j) Winged male of S. ramsayi, k) Wingless male of S. ramsayi, l) Female of S. ramsayi, m) Wingless male of S. domettensis, n) Female of S. domettensis, o) Wingless male of S. eylesi, p) Wingless male of S. stewartensis. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100756/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100764>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Locations where Stenosagola clarkei (black triangle), Stenosagola egmontensis (Black circle), Stenosagola ramsayi (black squares), Stenosagola domettensis (white circle), Stenosagola eylesi (star), and Stenosagola stewartensis (white square) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100764/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100779>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Locations where Stenosagola thayerae (triangles), Stenosagola dugdalei (circles), Stenosagola tararuaensis (squares), and Stenosagola haunuiensis (stars) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100773>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Locations where Stenosagola connata triangles), Stenosagola huiaensis (circles), and Stenosagola northlandensis (squares) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100773/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100783>
    dc:description "Fig. 13. Locations where Stenosagola pseudoconnata (triangles) and Stenosagola chandleri (squares) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100783/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100785>
    dc:description "Fig. 14. Locations where Stenosagola nunni (triangles), Stenosagola newtoni (circle), Stenosagola butcheri (black squares), and Stenosagola fiordlandensis (white square) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100785/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

